- Negative tests.
-- Whitespace in a String input raises BAD_ARGUMENTS.
-- Whitespace in an Array element raises BAD_ARGUMENTS.
-- Whitespace in a FixedString input raises BAD_ARGUMENTS.
-- Whitespace inside Array(Nullable(String)) raises BAD_ARGUMENTS.
-- Unsupported language raises ILLEGAL_TYPE_OF_ARGUMENT.
-- Wrong type for first argument raises ILLEGAL_TYPE_OF_ARGUMENT.
-- Wrong type for second argument raises ILLEGAL_TYPE_OF_ARGUMENT.
-- Tab character in a String input raises BAD_ARGUMENTS.
-- Newline character in a String input raises BAD_ARGUMENTS.
-- Array(UInt32) as first argument raises ILLEGAL_TYPE_OF_ARGUMENT.
-- Array(Nullable(UInt32)) as first argument raises ILLEGAL_TYPE_OF_ARGUMENT.
-- Array(Array(String)) as first argument raises ILLEGAL_TYPE_OF_ARGUMENT.
